---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="404 | Se lavó el mate">
	<section class="h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-4 relative overflow-hidden">
		
		<div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-mate-green/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>

		<div class="mb-8 relative grayscale opacity-80 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500">
             <svg width="120" height="120" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none">
                <path d="M20 30 C10 60 25 90 50 90 C75 90 90 60 80 30 H20 Z" fill="#262626" stroke="#404040" stroke-width="2"/>
                <ellipse cx="50" cy="30" rx="25" ry="3" fill="#333"/>
                <path d="M55 30 L80 -10" stroke="#666" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
             </svg>
		</div>

		<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold text-white font-mono mb-2">404</h1>
		<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-mate-green font-bold mb-6">Se lavó el mate.</h2>
		
		<p class="text-gray-400 max-w-md mb-10 leading-relaxed">
			La página que buscás no tiene agua, ni yerba, ni existe.
            <br>
            Probablemente escribiste mal la URL o me olvidé de cebar este link.
		</p>

		<a href="/" class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-mate-green hover:text-black hover:border-mate-green transition-all font-mono group flex items-center gap-2">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
			</svg>
			Volver a cebar (Inicio)
		</a>

	</section>
</Layout>